snippet.title: Used Cars Simulator - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Add To Your Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2637940/Used_Cars_Simulator/

🚗 Used Cars Simulator - trade used or stolen cars, fix and customize them, drive around, and explore the open world! 🌎 Grow your business, complete quests, and have fun with a physics-based sandbox! 🛠️💼🎮
